<div id="review_1619747540" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1619747540" />
    <a title="Maria Lucia Seidl de Moura" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/39667821-maria-lucia-seidl-de-moura"><img alt="Maria Lucia Seidl de Moura" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1520745238p2/39667821.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1619747540?book_show_action=true">Apr 24, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Maria Lucia Seidl de Moura" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Maria Lucia Seidl de Moura" href="/user/show/39667821-maria-lucia-seidl-de-moura">Maria Lucia Seidl de Moura</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/20124337-fire-under-the-snow">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1619747540" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16425979382014896206">This is a horrible story, but at the same time a wonderful one. It presents the horror that human beings can inflict to others, the evil that we are capable of. However, at the same time, and mostly, it is a book about resilience, about the indestructible core of love that Gyatso Palden is capable of and that he shares with us. It inspired me and reinforced my conviccion that there is only place for a Free Tibet! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


