<div id="review_1422082921" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1422082921" />
    <a title="Aaron Graves" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/37313966-aaron-graves"><img alt="Aaron Graves" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1567701448p2/37313966.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1422082921?book_show_action=true">Oct 21, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Aaron Graves" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Aaron Graves" href="/user/show/37313966-aaron-graves">Aaron Graves</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780802135742" href="/book/show/58335.The_Autobiography_of_a_Tibetan_Monk">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1422082921" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14566587720592456885">This book is a moving and powerful story about a Tibetan monk who endured the better part of his life in communist prisons within his native Tibet. I found myself unable to put the book down, as evidenced by the fact that I had it completed in about 24 hours (with several breaks in between).</span>

          </span>
        </div>


