<div id="review_2321816018" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2321816018" />
    <a title="Katerina" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12971190-katerina"><img alt="Katerina" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1529263227p2/12971190.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2321816018?book_show_action=true">Feb 13, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Katerina" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Katerina" href="/user/show/12971190-katerina">Katerina</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12971190-katerina?shelf=bookcrossing">bookcrossing</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2321816018" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12168896720685414323">I cannot possibly imagine all the immense sufferings Palden Gyatso has gone through during his time in prison. This book is incredibly difficult to read, as so many emotions arise. For us, Westerners, it seems almost impossible that somewhere in the world such oppressive regime still exists, and so many human beings suffer for no reason on a daily basis at the hands of vile perpetrators. Nevertheless, as difficult as it is to read, this book must be read by as many people as possible, to raise a</span>
  <span id="freeText12168896720685414323" style="display:none">I cannot possibly imagine all the immense sufferings Palden Gyatso has gone through during his time in prison. This book is incredibly difficult to read, as so many emotions arise. For us, Westerners, it seems almost impossible that somewhere in the world such oppressive regime still exists, and so many human beings suffer for no reason on a daily basis at the hands of vile perpetrators. Nevertheless, as difficult as it is to read, this book must be read by as many people as possible, to raise awareness about the situation in Tibet. I believe Palden Gyatso's sufferings and efforts were not in vain and that one day Tibet will be free.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12168896720685414323" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


